add this entry server Dnsname 
172.16.238.10:5003

Then restart Apache:
systemctl restart httpd

7Ô∏è‚É£ Open Port 5003 via iptables (Since firewalld Is Unavailable)

restart httpd service 
sudo systemctl restart httpd

üî• Open Port 5003 via iptables (since firewalld isn‚Äôt available)
